-- Gamesa Will Cut Cost of Wind Energy 30% in Next Five Years, Executive Says
-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 2010-10-07T12:55:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/gamesa-will-cut-cost-of-wind-energy-30-in-next-five-years-executive-says.html
Gamesa Corporacion Tecnologica SA
will reduce the cost of wind energy by 30 percent over the next
five years, Chief Technology Officer Jose Antonio Malumbres told
investors in London today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
